                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 5082/113.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Janes</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-02-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 21, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Janes says the Brazilian minister for foreign affairs offers his personal
                    congratulations on the signing of the protocol for the settlement of American
                    claims against Venezuela.</p>
            </div>
